  <entry>
    <title>Machine Learning</title>
    <link href="https://staticor.github.io/2019/03/03/machine-learning/"/>
    <id>https://staticor.github.io/2019/03/03/machine-learning/</id>
    <published>2019-03-03T02:23:42.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-03-05T13:17:35.737Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>假期找了几本关于机器学习的书，将一些比较重要的核心公式整体到这里。</p><h1 id="线性回归"><a href="#线性回归" class="headerlink" title="线性回归"></a>线性回归</h1><h2 id="模型描述"><a href="#模型描述" class="headerlink" title="模型描述"></a>模型描述</h2><p>特征空间假设， 寻找线性系数 $ \theta $ 以希望用一个线性函数逼近目标向量。</p><p>逼近的效果好坏叫做 <strong>Cost Function</strong>， 下面列出的MSE便是其中一种。</p><blockquote><p>Linear Regression</p></blockquote><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat y = h_{\theta} (x) =  \theta \cdot x</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">MSE(x, h_{\theta}) =  \frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^{m} ( \theta^T \cdot x^{(i)} - y^{(i)} )^2</script><h2 id="梯度下降"><a href="#梯度下降" class="headerlink" title="梯度下降"></a>梯度下降</h2><img src="/2019/03/03/machine-learning/sgd.png" title="sgd"><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\Theta^{(next step)} = \Theta - \eta \nabla_\theta MSE( \theta )</script><p>其中 </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\nabla_\theta MSE( \theta ) = \begin{pmatrix}\frac{\partial}{\partial_{\theta_0}} MSE( \theta ) \\\frac{\partial}{\partial_{\theta_1}} MSE( \theta ) \\\cdots \\\frac{\partial}{\partial_{\theta_n}} MSE( \theta ) \\\end{pmatrix} = \frac{2}{m} X^T (X\Theta - Y)</script><h2 id="带有正则项"><a href="#带有正则项" class="headerlink" title="带有正则项"></a>带有正则项</h2><ul><li>Ridge Regression</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J(\theta) = MSE(\theta) + \alpha \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i=1}^{n} \theta_i^2</script><img src="/2019/03/03/machine-learning/ridge.png" title="ridge"><ul><li>LASSO</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J(\theta) = MSE(\theta) + \alpha \sum_{i=1}^{n} | \theta_i |</script><ul><li>Elastic Net</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J(\theta) = MSE(\theta) + r \alpha \sum_{i=1}^{n} | \theta_i | + \frac{1-r}{2} \alpha  \sum_{i=1}^{n} \theta_i^2</script><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>sklearn-线性回归</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.linear_model <span class="keyword">import</span> LinearRegression</span><br><span class="line">lr = LinearRegression()</span><br><span class="line">lr.fit(X, y)</span><br><span class="line">lr.intercept_, lr.coef_</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#mse</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.metrics <span class="keyword">import</span> mean_squared_error</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># sgd</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.linear_model <span class="keyword">import</span> SGDRegressor</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="对数线性回归-Logistic-Regression"><a href="#对数线性回归-Logistic-Regression" class="headerlink" title="对数线性回归 - Logistic Regression"></a>对数线性回归 - Logistic Regression</h2><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\hat p = h_\theta (x) = \sigma (\theta^T x)</script><p>$ \sigma(t) $ 是Sigmoid函数</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\sigma (t) =  \frac{1}{1 + exp(-t) }</script><p>Logistic Regression cost function (log loss)</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J(\theta) = - \frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^{m} [y^{(i)} log( { \hat p }^(i) )   +  (1-y^{(i)})log( 1-{\hat p}^i)  ]</script><p>Logistic cost function partial derivatives </p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\frac{\partial}{\partial \theta_j } J(\boldsymbol \theta) = \frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^{m} ( \sigma ( \boldsymbol \theta^T x^i ) -y^i ) x_j^i</script><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>sklearn-Logistic Regression</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.linear_model <span class="keyword">import</span> LogisticRegression</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">log_reg = LogisticRegression()</span><br><span class="line">log_reg.fit(X, y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Softmax-Regression"><a href="#Softmax-Regression" class="headerlink" title="Softmax Regression"></a>Softmax Regression</h2><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\widehat p_k = \sigma ( \boldsymbol s(x))_k   = \frac{exp(s_k(\boldsymbol x))}{ \sum_{j=1}^K exp(s_j(\boldsymbol x))}</script><h1 id="支持向量机"><a href="#支持向量机" class="headerlink" title="支持向量机"></a>支持向量机</h1><blockquote><p>Support Vector Machine</p></blockquote><ul><li>Decision Functions and Predictions</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\widehat{y} = \begin{cases}0, &  {if \quad w^T x + b > 0 } \\1, &  {if \quad w^T x + b \leq 0 } \\\end{cases}</script><ul><li>Hard Margin Classification</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\min_{w, b} \frac{1}{2} w^T \cdot w</script><p>subject to</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">t^{(i)} (w^T x^{(i)} + b) \geq 1   ,\quad   for \quad i = 1,2, \cdots , m</script><ul><li>Soft Margin Classification</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\min_{w, b} \frac{1}{2} w^T \cdot w  + C \sum_{i=1}^m \xi^{(i)}</script><p>subject to</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">t^{(i)} (w^T x^{(i)} + b) \geq 1 - \xi^{(i)}  and \quad  \xi^{(i)} \geq 0 , \quad   for \quad i = 1,2, \cdots , m</script><ul><li>Dual Problem</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\min_{ \alpha }    \frac{1}{2} \sum_{i=1}^m \sum_{j=1}^m \alpha^{(i)} \alpha^{(j)} t^{(i)} t^{(j)} {x^{(i)}}^T \cdot x^{(j)}  - \sum_{i=1}^m \alpha^{(i)}</script><p>subject to</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\alpha^{(i)} \geq 0   \quad  for \quad i = 1,2, \cdots , m</script><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>LinearSVC</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn <span class="keyword">import</span> datasets</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.pipeline <span class="keyword">import</span> Pipeline</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.preprocessing <span class="keyword">import</span> StandardScaler</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.svm <span class="keyword">import</span> LinearSVC</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">iris = datasets.load_iris()</span><br><span class="line">X = iris[<span class="string">"data"</span>][:, (<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>)]  <span class="comment"># petal length, petal width</span></span><br><span class="line">y = (iris[<span class="string">"target"</span>] == <span class="number">2</span>).astype(np.float64)  <span class="comment"># Iris-Virginica</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">svm_clf = Pipeline([</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="string">"scaler"</span>, StandardScaler()),</span><br><span class="line">        (<span class="string">"linear_svc"</span>, LinearSVC(C=<span class="number">1</span>, loss=<span class="string">"hinge"</span>)),</span><br><span class="line">    ])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">svm_clf.fit(X, y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Common-kernels"><a href="#Common-kernels" class="headerlink" title="Common kernels"></a>Common kernels</h2><ul><li>Linear</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">K(\boldsymbol a, \boldsymbol b)  = \boldsymbol a^T \cdot \boldsymbol b</script><ul><li>Polynomial</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">K(\boldsymbol a, \boldsymbol b)  =  ( \gamma \boldsymbol a^T \cdot \boldsymbol b + r)^d</script><ul><li>Gaussian RBF</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">K(\boldsymbol a, \boldsymbol b)  =  exp(- \gamma || \boldsymbol a - \boldsymbol b|| ^2 )</script><ul><li>Sigmoid</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">K(\boldsymbol a, \boldsymbol b)  =  tanh( \gamma \boldsymbol a^T \cdot \boldsymbol b + r)</script><h1 id="树"><a href="#树" class="headerlink" title="树"></a>树</h1><blockquote><p>从树到森林。</p><p>Decision Tree </p></blockquote><h2 id="Decision-Trees"><a href="#Decision-Trees" class="headerlink" title="Decision Trees"></a>Decision Trees</h2><ul><li>Gini impurity</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">G_i = 1 - \sum_{k=1}^n p_{i,k}^2</script><ul><li>Entropy</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">H_i = - \sum_{k=1,\\ p_{i,k} \ne 0}^n p_{i,k} log_2 (p_{i,k})</script><ul><li>CART cost function for regression</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">J(k, t_k) = \frac{m_{left}}{m} MSE_{left}+ \frac{m_{right}}{m} MSE_{right}</script><p>where</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{cases}MSE_{node} = \sum_{i \in node} ( \hat y_{node} - y^{(i)} )^2 \\ \hat y_{node} = \frac{1}{m_{node}} \sum_{i \in node} y^{(i)}   \\\end{cases}</script><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>DecisionTreeClassifier</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.datasets <span class="keyword">import</span> load_iris</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.tree <span class="keyword">import</span> DecisionTreeClassifier</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">iris = load_iris()</span><br><span class="line">X = iris.data[:, <span class="number">2</span>:] <span class="comment"># petal length and width</span></span><br><span class="line">y = iris.target</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tree_clf = DecisionTreeClassifier(max_depth=<span class="number">2</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tree_clf.fit(X, y)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Random-Forests"><a href="#Random-Forests" class="headerlink" title="Random Forests"></a>Random Forests</h2><p>RF 在我看来是 Ensemble Learning (集成学习)的经典代表。</p><p>以Classifiers举例，对待同样的数据， 不同分类器可能有不同的决策结果。 </p><p><em>Logistic Regression classifier</em>, <em>Random Forest classifier</em>, <em>K-Nearest Neighbors classifier</em></p><p>自然而然的， 可引入选举策略来作最终决策。</p><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>voting of classifier</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.ensemble <span class="keyword">import</span> RandomForestClassifier</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.ensemble <span class="keyword">import</span> VotingClassifier</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.linear_model <span class="keyword">import</span> LogisticRegression</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.svm <span class="keyword">import</span> SVC</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">log_clf = LogisticRegression()</span><br><span class="line">rnd_clf = RandomForestClassifier()</span><br><span class="line">svm_clf = SVC()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">voting_clf = VotingClassifier(</span><br><span class="line">    estimators=[(<span class="string">'lr'</span>, log_clf), (<span class="string">'rf'</span>, rnd_clf), (<span class="string">'svc'</span>, svm_clf)],</span><br><span class="line">    voting=<span class="string">'hard'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">voting_clf.fit(X_train, y_train)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Boosting"><a href="#Boosting" class="headerlink" title="Boosting"></a>Boosting</h2><h3 id="Adaboost"><a href="#Adaboost" class="headerlink" title="Adaboost"></a>Adaboost</h3><h3 id="Gradient-Boosting"><a href="#Gradient-Boosting" class="headerlink" title="Gradient Boosting"></a>Gradient Boosting</h3><h1 id="效果指标"><a href="#效果指标" class="headerlink" title="效果指标"></a>效果指标</h1><p>确定Model收敛的方向， 对连续和离散模型都有若干种<em>Metrics</em> </p><h2 id="Classification"><a href="#Classification" class="headerlink" title="Classification"></a>Classification</h2><script type="math/tex; mode=display">precision = \frac{TP}{TP+FP}</script><script type="math/tex; mode=display">recall = \frac{TP}{TP+FN}</script><p>$F_1$ 是二者的调和平均</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">F_1 = \frac{2}{\frac{1}{precision} + \frac{1}{recall}}</script><figure class="highlight python"><figcaption><span>precision_score and recall_score</span></figcaption><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> sklearn.metrics <span class="keyword">import</span> precision_score, recall_score</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="Regression"><a href="#Regression" class="headerlink" title="Regression"></a>Regression</h2><ul><li>MSE</li></ul><script type="math/tex; mode=display">MSE(x, h_{\theta}) =  \frac{1}{m} \sum_{i=1}^{m} ( \theta^T \cdot x^{(i)} - y^{(i)} )^2</script>]]></content>
    
